# SOC Level 1 - Log Analysis with SIEM

This repository documents **hands-on SOC Level 1 investigations** conducted using **Splunk SIEM** in the *TryHackMe â€“ Log Analysis with SIEM* lab. The focus of this portfolio is **alert triage, log investigation, and escalation-style analysis**, mirroring real-world blue team responsibilities in a Security Operations Centre.

> **Role Focus:** SOC Analyst Level 1 | Defensive Security | Monitoring & Triage

